==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: manganic acid
<hw>manganic acid</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A dibasic acid
<chform>H2MnO4</chform>, formed from manganese, analogous to sulphuric
acid; it is found only in solution and in manganate salts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Manganiferous</ent>⟦br⟧
